title: The George Foreman 5-Serving Classic Plate Grill
description: Create nutritious meals in minutes for the whole family with the George Foreman 80-sq in Grill. Its patented slope helps knock out the fat as you cook. A nonstick coating lets you cook oil-free, while the variable temperature control allows for precise cooking versatility. This grill features an adjustable cooking height hinge for cooking juicy burgers or thick sandwiches. The dishwasher-safe grease tray helps make cleanup a snap.

transcripts: George Foreman simple grilling satisfaction the George Foreman 5 serving grill creates delicious meals for the whole family variable temperature controls allow for precision controlled cooking for meat and vegetables or toasting up a panini and the dual grilling services let you cook in half the time it takes to pan fry keep it low fat with whatever you're grilling the George tough non-stick grilling surface removes the need for access oil and butter plus it's durable and easy to wipe clean the one-inch floating hinge allows for even cooking of thick cuts of meat and sandwiches and the adjustable leg allows you to grill on sloped are flat surfaces remove up to 42 percent of fat using the slope surface when you grill meat and burgers. Dual indicator lights show when the grill is plugged in and when it's preheated which typically takes just five-minutes. The George Foreman 5 serving grill reliable grilling for fast tasty meals.
